{"tid":1854023,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google宣布將捐款超700萬元並上線病情專題界面提供官方權威信息","createTime":"2020-01-31T09:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T18:16:02.000Z","uid":85180,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0373cd4422eaddf94385e2e941cc8c549cff1d29","tid":1854023,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:40:56.000Z","msg":"Google宣布將捐款超700萬元並上線病情專題界面提供官方權威信息<br />\n今日，<a href=\"http://Google宣布其慈善組織Google.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoogle%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%85%B6%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94Google.org&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=8e012e8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Google宣布其慈善組織Google.org</a>將為中國紅十字會提供25萬美元的直接捐助用於支持新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情的防控工作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/spider2020131/239/w600h439/20200131/2724-intiarp6135845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider2020131%2F239%2Fw600h439%2F20200131%2F2724-intiarp6135845.jpg&h=cdb58b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除此之外，谷歌還發起了一項內部活動，號召谷歌員工為此捐款。截止目前，通過內部捐贈，谷歌已經籌集了超過80萬美元的資金，總計約合728萬元人民幣的善款將一併捐助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/spider2020131/48/w600h248/20200131/d3c3-intiarp6135841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider2020131%2F48%2Fw600h248%2F20200131%2Fd3c3-intiarp6135841.jpg&h=a8be0357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，谷歌已經將&ldquo;coronavirus&rdquo;（冠狀病毒）的搜索結果調整，用於其SOS警報機制中。現在，用戶搜索&ldquo;coronavirus&rdquo;（冠狀病毒）相關詞條後，將進入谷歌精心挑選的搜索結果頁面，其中包含世界衛生組織，中國疾病預防控制中心等權威機構的一手信息，資源、安全提示和新聞更新等，方便用戶第一時間了解到最權威的信息報導。<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/spider2020131/250/w600h450/20200131/7d5a-intiarp6135894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider2020131%2F250%2Fw600h450%2F20200131%2F7d5a-intiarp6135894.jpg&h=19077913&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2882a8e9136ee8fbf0e9c5c98643bbeef3b37c74","tid":1854023,"uid":235824,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"捐俾中國紅十字會..... google 都幾撚ON9"},{"pid":"e2ab4ad41aec604901dcb06682d3090f6dcd3983","tid":1854023,"uid":79869,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:44:42.000Z","msg":"中國紅十字會 = 中國官方指定貪污機構<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1853204/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1853204/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ce795c445953d94b77e97f01db399a090a11fbc3","tid":1854023,"uid":8880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/google_comms/status/1222991299667587073?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgoogle_comms%2Fstatus%2F1222991299667587073%3Fs%3D21&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=f15faa04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgoogle_comms%2Fstatus%2F1222991299667587073%3Fs%3D21&h=1a541f86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/google_comms/status/1222991299667587073?s=21</a><br />\n入去屌柒佢 捐錢俾貪污機構"},{"pid":"1d8ad9226072654e144a1a88eaa7c00a8dff4c58","tid":1854023,"uid":109923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:47:34.000Z","msg":"中國紅十字fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOn9 無極限 支那山東捐武漢350噸蔬菜 被支那紅會賣超市收錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1852545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1852545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7bbda0b62d39a4eb22d219b9cd44f9cfc2943147","tid":1854023,"uid":5523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2882a8e9136ee8fbf0e9c5c98643bbeef3b37c74","tid":1854023,"uid":235824,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"捐俾中國紅十字會..... google 都幾撚ON9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"商業決定姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p